<div class="primary colored section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><img class="icon" src="images/logos/icon.svg" />What is <%= application.name %>?</h2>

			<div class="well">
				<b>kitty</b> (noun): a collection of goods often made up of small contributions
			</div>

			<p><%= application.name %> is a cloud-based geospatial image and data storage, management, and sharing system. Best of all, you can run it on your own server. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/info/desktop/desktop.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="<%= application.name %>"><img src="images/info/desktop/desktop.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption"><%= application.name %></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-dollar-sign"></i>It's Free!</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> is <a href="#policies/terms-of-use">free to use</a> for non-commmercial applications.  It's also <a href="#downloads">free to download</a> and run on your own server. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<a href="#downloads">
					<img style="width:150px" src="images/logos/icon.svg" />
				</a>
				<div class="caption"><i class="fa fa-heart" style="color:hotpink; margin-right:5px"></i>Adopt Me!</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-fire"></i>It's Easy to Launch</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> makes it <a href="#installation">quick and easy to launch</a> your own personal, customized <%= application.name %> on your own server. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<a href="#downloads">
					<img height="175px" src="images/logos/rocketkitty-icon.svg" />
				</a>
				<div class="caption">
					Launch Me!
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-image"></i>Map Your Travel Photos</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> will display your geolocated images and videos on a map.  Visualize and relive your travel adventures geospatially. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<img height="200px" src="images/welcome/globe-icon.svg" />
				<img height="100px" src="images/welcome/travel-kitty-photo.svg" style="transform:rotate(-30); margin-left:-100px" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-helicopter"></i>Map Your Aerial Images</h2>
			<p>For drone pilots, <%= application.name %> provides a convenient way to manage and visualize your aerial data and share data with collaborators and customers. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<img height="200px" src="images/welcome/aerial-drone.svg" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-folder"></i>Map Your Data</h2>
			<p>Assign a geolocation to any file or folder.  View your files and folders as either a traditional file hierarchy or as a map.  <%= application.name %> is a geospatial operating system. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure" style="width:200px; position:relative">
				<img width="200px" src="images/welcome/map-icon.svg" />

				<div class="icon-grid figure" style="position:absolute; margin-left:20px; margin-top:-125px">
					<div class="directory item">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="icon"><img src="images/icons/folders/folder-full.svg" /></div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="name" style="color:white;font-weight:bold">Site1</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="icon-grid figure" style="position:absolute; margin-left:80px; margin-top:-170px">
					<div class="directory item">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="icon"><img src="images/icons/folders/folder-full.svg" /></div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="name" style="color:white;font-weight:bold">Site2</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-globe"></i>Map Your Environment</h2>
			<p> <%= application.name %> can help you to track environmental data and to monitor your environment for changes and trends.  Use <%= application.name %> to help with your research in environmental and sustainability issues. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<img width="200px" src="images/welcome/globe-icon.svg" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Share Your Maps</h2>
			<p>Share your maps and geodata with friends, family, and colleagues. <%= application.name %> makes it easy to share geospatial information. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure" style="width:400px">
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F46E.svg" />
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F468.svg" />
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F469.svg" />
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F471.svg" />
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F474.svg" />
				<img width="75px" style="margin:15px" src="images/welcome/sharing/1F477.svg" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<h2><i class="fa fa-tools"></i>Take Back Control</h2>
			<p>You no longer need to give up control over your geodata just to get access to a technology platform. By running your own <%= application.name %>, you control the platform and your geodata. Join the <a href="#features/host-it-yourself">host it yourself (HIY)</a> movement and take back control over your (digital) life! </p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="figure">
				<a href="#welcome/we-can-do-it">
					<img class="vertical" src="images/welcome/we-can-do-it.jpg" />
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>